```python
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

df_trade = pd.DataFrame({
    "trade_id": [1,2,3,4,5,6],
    "symbol":   ["AAA","AAA","AAA","BBB","BBB","BBB"],
    "ts": pd.to_datetime([
        "2025-12-01 09:00",
        "2025-12-01 09:03",
        "2025-12-01 09:07",
        "2025-12-01 09:01",
        "2025-12-01 09:04",
        "2025-12-01 09:08",
    ]),
    "side": ["BUY","BUY","SELL","BUY","SELL","SELL"],
    "qty":  [10,   20,   15,   5,    10,   20],
    "exec_px":[101, 103,  99,  201,  198,  195]
})

df_quote = pd.DataFrame({
    "symbol": ["AAA"]*5 + ["BBB"]*5,
    "ts": pd.to_datetime([
        "2025-12-01 08:59",
        "2025-12-01 09:02",
        "2025-12-01 09:05",
        "2025-12-01 09:06",
        "2025-12-01 09:09",
        "2025-12-01 09:00",
        "2025-12-01 09:03",
        "2025-12-01 09:05",
        "2025-12-01 09:07",
        "2025-12-01 09:09",
    ]),
    "mid_px":[100, 102, 101, 100, 98,  200, 199, 197, 196, 194]
})
display(df_trade, df_quote)
```

# ÌíÄÏù¥

```python
df_merged = pd.merge_asof(df_trade.sort_values(by='ts'), df_quote.sort_values(by='ts'), on='ts', by='symbol')
display(df_merged)
df_merged['slippage_bps'] = np.where(df_merged['side']=='BUY',(df_merged['exec_px']-df_merged['mid_px'])/df_merged['mid_px']*10000, (df_merged['mid_px']-df_merged['exec_px'])/df_merged['mid_px']*10000)
df_merged['is_bad']=df_merged['slippage_bps']>=120
display(df_merged)
sym_feat = (
    df_merged
    .assign(weighted_slip = df_merged['slippage_bps'] * df_merged['qty'])
    .groupby('symbol', as_index=False)
    .agg(
        trades=('trade_id','count'),
        bad_trades=('is_bad','sum'),
        slip_bps_mean=('slippage_bps','mean'),
        weighted_sum=('weighted_slip','sum'),
        qty_sum=('qty','sum')
    )
)

sym_feat['slip_bps_wavg'] = sym_feat['weighted_sum'] / sym_feat['qty_sum']
sym_feat = sym_feat.drop(columns=['weighted_sum','qty_sum']).sort_values(by='slip_bps_wavg', ascending=False)
display(sym_feat)
```

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
fig1, axs =plt.subplots(nrows=2, ncols=1, figsize=(7,6))
symbols = ['AAA','BBB']
for idx, symbol in enumerate(symbols):
    r = df_merged[df_merged['symbol']==symbol]
    axs[idx].plot(r['ts'],r['slippage_bps'])
    axs[idx].scatter(r[r['is_bad']]['ts'], r[r['is_bad']]['slippage_bps'], color='red')
    axs[idx].axhline(120, color = 'gray', linestyle='--')
    axs[idx].grid(False)
    axs[idx].set_title(f'{symbol} Slippage')
    axs[idx].set_xlabel('ts')
    axs[idx].set_ylabel('slippage_bps')
fig2, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(7,4))
for idx, symbol in enumerate(symbols):
    r= sym_feat[sym_feat['symbol']==symbol]
    ax.bar(r['symbol'], r['slip_bps_wavg'])
ax.axhline(120, color = 'gray', linestyle='--')
ax.set_title("Weighted Avg Slippage (bps)")
ax.set_xlabel('symbol')
ax.set_ylabel('slip_bps_wavg')
ax.grid(False)
plt.show()
```
